It can be treated as a basic graph modelling question.
We have two arrays in and out to calculate the indegrees of vertices ( people of the town) 
A person is only a Judge if he is trusted by everybody ( or the out[i] should be equal to N -1 , where N is the total number of people ) and he does not trust anybody ( or the in[i] should be equal to 0 ).
Hope it helps :)
