We solve this problem in 2 steps. First, calculate the number of people that trust a person `i`, and also the number of people the person `i` trusts to. Then, on the second step, we iterate over all people and check for which person all conditions are satisfied.

Time: **O(n)** - scan
Space: **O(n)** - hashmaps

