Simply we have to check if there is an elemnt from 1 to n which doesnot trust on nobody so check its occurence is zero in left half i.e trust[i][0] and second thing check if its occurence in second half i.e trust[i][1] is n-1 beacuse all other n-1 should trust on him if these two conditions are there then we have Judge else -1.
# Approach
