Two Conditions:
- Check in trust[i][0]'s which element has 0 occurence because judge dont trust of anybody so use a map and check .Also if greater than one people are there who have 0 occurence then ans is -1 because Judge can be only one .
- After getting this element check in trust array i.e on right side trust[i][1]'s if its occurence is n-1 if yes return that element if not -1.
